    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Shopping List — Periodic Reconciliation\n\nRuns every 15 minutes to catch missed events and keep\nMealie and Home Assistant shopping lists in sync.\n\n**Flow:**\n1. Fetch ALL items from Mealie and HA in parallel\n2. Compare by normalized item name\n3. Add missing items to whichever system is missing them\n4. Resolve status mismatches (Mealie = source of truth)\n\n**Environment variables used:**\n- `MEALIE_URL` — Mealie base URL\n- `MEALIE_API_TOKEN` — Mealie API Token\n- `HA_URL` — Home Assistant base URL  \n- `HOMEASSISTANT_API_TOKEN` — HA Long-Lived Access Token\n\n**Notes:**\n- Mealie is source of truth for checked/unchecked status\n- Only truly missing items are added (idempotent)\n- No action taken if both lists are already in sync",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 420
      },
